# Upstream Mirror Workflow

This repository is an extracted mirror of:
`flutter/packages/packages/webview_flutter/webview_flutter_wkwebview`

## Mapping

- Treat this repository root as equivalent to the upstream subdirectory above.
- Do not introduce a nested `webview_flutter_wkwebview/` folder at repo root.

## Syncing Upstream Into Local Changes

- If updating from upstream, refresh the extracted WKWebView branch from
  `flutter/packages` and integrate it here.
- Prefer rebasing local work on top of refreshed upstream extracted history.
- If user explicitly prefers no history rewrite, use merge instead of rebase.

## Upstream PR Expectations

- This repo is for isolated plugin work; upstream PRs target `flutter/packages`.
- When preparing upstream submissions, place changes under:
  `packages/webview_flutter/webview_flutter_wkwebview`

## Safety and Confirmation

- Ask before force-pushes or destructive history operations.
- When uncertain, preserve user commits and avoid dropping local changes.
